        "content": "**Q:** A and B together can do a job in 10 days. A alone can do it in 15 days. In how many days can B alone complete the job?\n**Solution:** (A + B)'s 1-day work = 1/10, A's 1-day = 1/15\n⇒ B's 1-day = 1/10 − 1/15 = (3 − 2)/30 = 1/30\n**Answer:** 30 days"
